I am only giving this package 3 stars not because of the quality of the series but because of the packaging.  I love CSI and I am enjoying my guilty pleasure of watching an episode or two before going to bed.  Unfortunately, the plastic holders easily break away from the binding and once you pop out the disc, it is difficult to put it back in.  For some reason the discs do not seem to want to stick back onto the small ring holder.  It often requires a great deal of manipulation to secure the disc back into the holder and I am afraid I will crack the disc.

I have all of the complete series of CSI:Las Vegas a real good show. It aired on CBS from October 2nd 2000-September 27th 2015 for 15 seasons, 341 episodes it also includes a bonus 1 Without A Trace crossover episode during the 8th season, 1 CSI:Miami, 2 CSI:New York crossover episodes during the 10th season and  the 13th season. CSI:Las Vegas is still one of the greatest TV shows in the history of television!! Thank god I have all of the complete series including the finale!!
